<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>GUIDE ME !</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lalpa Jeho, Nang ei Puipa,
 Gam thiengtho ah ei tun in;
 Kei ka hatpuoi, ei Panpihpa,
 Na khut thahat in ei tu'n.

[V2]
 Hinna Changthak (2)
 Ka ngai hi ei vak zing in (2)

[V3]
 2. Tuikhuk chîmtak chu hun hawng in,
 Damna tui luonsak inla;
 Zie gamgaw gam ka kân sung hin,
 Nang in ei puizel inla.

[V4]
 3. Jordan luipi ka kân tieng leh,
 Ka thavaihna suhai in;
 Ka masawm gam Kanaan achun,
 Bit takin ei tun inla.
 Chawih-atna la (2)
 Kumkhawsawt in sa ta'ng ka (2)</lyrics>
<hymn_number>13</hymn_number>
</song>